       - index.html -> push to GitHub + enable Pages OR drag to Netlify / Vercel
       - Formspree: as long as endpoint https://formspree.io/f/xnnbnjay is active, wiadomości trafią na Twój formularz
       - If you want an instant "thank-you" redirect instead of modal, add <input name="_next" value="https://twoja-strona/thanks"> inside form
  -->

